explanation: The loop only iterated for i in range(6) (i = 0..5), so the case where N is between 10^8 and 10^9-1 (which requires i = 6) was never handled and large inputs produced no output. I fixed it by extending the loop to range(7) so i runs 0..6 and the final case is covered. This is analogous to the style of fixes that increase an upper bound in a range (see Diff 5 pattern).
